{"title":"高举祝酒杯——俳句","authors":["沙蕾"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":1,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举祝酒杯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——俳句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙  蕾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝暾天下辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八十年代登舞台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举祝酒杯："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“愿和风习习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正义大旗寰宇飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海歌声闹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不许豺狼嗥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口诛笔伐腾怒涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪流淹邪妖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“愿祖国兴旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百家争鸣旋律好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百花齐舞蹈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“新长征途中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民主、科学双翼牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高翔冲九霄！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众人皆碰杯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杯声琅琅迸欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共饮时代潮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）俳句是日本诗体之一。一般以三句十七音组成一首短诗，首句五音，次句七音，末句五音，又称十七音诗。本诗则每节采用日本的俳句形式。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}